media:group.media:title: Season's Beatings
media:group.media:description: A small project I did a while back showcasing some very amateur 2D Animation.   I attempted a parody on the "Matrix Kick" and tried to emulate the look of vintage cartoons.  My drawings were very rookie at the time, since then I have improved tremendously over the years.  This is my first ever cartoon.  Enjoy!
